ext-8xl text-ays-ink\">Engineering quantum computing for<!-- --> <span class=\"text-ays-brand\">real-world deployment.</span></h1><p class=\"mt-10 lg:mt-14 max-w-[58ch] text-lg lg:text-xl text-ays-ink/70 leading-[1.55]\">Anyon Systems is building the next generation of quantum computing infrastructure: designed not just for research, but for <strong class=\"font-bold text-ays-ink\">real-world deployment</strong>. Founded in Canada in 2014, the company pioneered the country\u2019s <strong class=\"font-bold text-ays-ink\">first universal gate-based quantum computers</strong> and continues to advance sovereign quantum capabilities while serving a global market.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 lg:gap-6 lg:aspect-2/1\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden lg:col-span-1 aspect-4/3 lg:aspect-auto\"><img src=\"/assets/site-images/office-external/office-external-04.jpg?v=cfc17f3\" alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover\"></div><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden lg:col-span-2 aspect-3/2 lg:aspect-auto\"><img src=\"/assets/site-images/office-external/office-external-11.jpg?v=cfc17f3\" alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover\"></div></div></div><div class=\"max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 pt-20 lg:pt-28 pb-20 lg:pb-32\"><p class=\"mx-auto max-w-[58ch] text-center text-lg lg:text-xl text-ays-ink/70 leading-[1.55]\">Anyon Systems has demonstrated its ability to <strong class=\"font-bold text-ays-ink\">deliver operational quantum hardware into real-world environments</strong>, including the deployment of its MonarQ system within Calcul Qu\u00e9bec\u2019s HPC ecosystem. Today, the company provides <strong class=\"font-bold text-ays-ink\">fully integrated, ready-to-use quantum platforms</strong> that combine hardware, software, and deployment expertise: enabling immediate use by research institutions, government programs, and enterprise partners in high-performance computing environments worldwide.</p></div></section><section class=\"bg-linear-150 from-ays-brand/5 to-white\"><div class=\"max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-20 lg:py-28\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-4\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-7\"><h2 class=\"max-w-[14ch] font-ays-display font-light tracking-ays-tightest leading-none text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl text-ays-ink\">Built for Real Environments</h2><p class=\"mt-8 lg:mt-12 max-w-[58ch] text-lg lg:text-xl text-ays-ink/70 leading-[1.55]\">Anyon Systems designs, builds, and commercializes full-stack superconducting quantum computers for real operational environments.</p></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-4 space-y-10 lg:space-y-12\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-base text-ays-ink/75 leading-relaxed\">Anyon is focused on practical quantum deployment today while engineering the path toward fault-tolerant quantum computing.</p><a href=\"/en/technology\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-ays-brand bg-white text-ays-brand font-ays-display text-sm font-normal px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-ays-brand hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200 ease-in\">Explore the technology<svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"M13 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-base text-ays-ink/75 leading-relaxed\">The company has already demonstrated the ability to deliver operational quantum hardware into high-performance computing environments, including MonarQ, deployed in Calcul Qu\u00e9bec\u2019s HPC ecosystem.</p><a href=\"/en/news\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-ays-brand bg-white text-ays-brand font-ays-display text-sm font-normal px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-ays-br